<h1>
    <a style="color: white" href="http://localhost/ezdoor/" class="nounderline">Home</a> <br>
    <font style="color: purple">Doors</font>
</h1>


<body bgcolor="blue"> <br><br> <br>
<div id="DoorArray">
    <left style="color: coral"> All Doors:</left>
    <table border="1px">
        <tr>
            <th>All Doors:</th>
        </tr>
        {% for p in text %}
            <tr>
                <td>{{ p.DoorId }}</td>
            </tr>
        {% endfor %}
    </table>
</div>

<div id="AddDoor"> Here you can add a door, with a new id:
    <form action="http://localhost/Ezdoor/Doors.php" method="post"> <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>
        Door id: <input type="text" name="Add door"> <br><br><br><br>
        <input type="text" name="DoorAdd">
        <input type="submit" value="Add Door">
    </form>
</div>

<div id="DeleteDoor"> Here you can delete a door from the database, by typing its id(number): <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>
    <form action="http://localhost/Ezdoor/Doors.php" method="post">
        Delete door by id: <input type="text" name="Delete"> <br><br><br><br>


        <input type="submit" value="Delete Door">
    </form>
</div>

<div id="EditDoor"> You can edit the number of the door here. Simply type your old door number and set in the new door number below: <br><br><br><br>
    <form action="http://localhost/Ezdoor/Doors.php" method="post">
        Old number: <input type="text" name="Oldnr"><br><br><br>
        New number: <input type="text" name="Newnr"> <br><br><br><br><br>

        <input type="submit" value="Edit Door">
    </form>
</div>
</body>